videos.headline: App State takes the early lead over Tennessee
videos.description: It's still early, but Appalachian State has upset on the mind as Taylor Lamb scores from five yards out to put the Mountaineers ahead of Tennessee.

videos.headline: Cox's diving TD puts App State up 13-3 on Tennessee
videos.description: Marcus Cox makes the tough catch and then finishes off the play with a dive over a defender into the end zone to increase Appalachian State's lead to 13-3 over Tennessee.

videos.headline: Tennessee recovers Dobbs' fumble in the end zone to take OT lead
videos.description: On the opening drive of overtime, Joshua Dobbs dives for the goalline but gets hit and fumbles into the end zone where Tennessee recovers for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Tennessee bats down App State's last gasp chance in OT
videos.description: On fourth down, Taylor Lamb's pass into the end zone is knocked away by Micah Abernathy and Appalachian State falls to Tennessee 20-13.

videos.headline: No. 9 Tennessee survives scare from Appalachian State
videos.description: Appalachian State takes a 13-3 lead into halftime, but Tennessee rallies to force overtime where Joshua Dobbs gets hit hard and fumbles the ball at the goal line but Jalen Hurd is there for the touchdown to lift the Volunteers to a 20-13 victory.
